        </h2>

        <div class="bg-[#F5521A]/5 border-l-4 border-[#F5521A] p-6 my-8">
          <p class="text-gray-900 font-black text-lg mb-2">If you're a complete beginner:</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Durable AI</strong> is the easiest. Enter your business name, get a complete website in 30 seconds. No learning curve, no tech skills needed.<br /><br />
            <strong>Framer AI</strong> if you care about design quality. Slightly more control, still beginner-friendly.<br /><br />
            <strong>10Web AI</strong> only if you specifically want WordPress. WordPress adds complexity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 id="top-picks" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Top 3 AI Builders for Beginners</h2>

        {tools.map(tool => (
          <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-[#F5521A]/20 p-8 my-8 hover:shadow-[0_8px_0_0_rgba(245,82,26,0.15)] transition-all">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <div>
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-[#F5521A] text-white font-black text-xs uppercase mb-2">
                  <span>â˜…</span>
                  <span>Beginner Pick</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900">{tool.name}</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#F5521A] font-medium mt-1">{tool.rating}</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-gray-700 my-4">{tool.why}</p>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-900 uppercase mb-2">Details</p>
                <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
                  <li><strong>Ease:</strong> {tool.ease}</li>
                  <li><strong>Speed:</strong> {tool.speed}</li>
                  <li><strong>Price:</strong> {tool.price}</li>
                  <li><strong>Best For:</strong> {tool.bestFor}</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

            <a href={tool.link} class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[#F5521A] font-black hover:underline">
              Try {tool.name.split(' ')[0]} â†’
            </a>
          </div>
        ))}

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">What Makes a Builder Beginner-Friendly?</h2>

        {beginnerFeatures.map(feature => (
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 my-6 p-4 bg-gray-50 border-[3px] border-gray-200">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              {feature.importance === 'Essential' && <span class="text-2xl">ðŸ”¥</span>}
              {feature.importance === 'Important' && <span class="text-2xl">âœ“</span>}
              {feature.importance === 'Nice to have' && <span class="text-2xl">â—‹</span>}
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900">{feature.feature}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">{feature.description}</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-[#F5521A] font-medium mt-1">{feature.importance}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Beginner-Friendly Comparison</h2>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto my-8">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-300">
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-600 font-medium">Criteria</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900 font-black">Durable AI</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900 font-black">Framer AI</th>
                <th class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900 font-black">10Web AI</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {comparison.map(row => (
                <tr class="border-b border-gray-300">
                  <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900 font-medium">{row.criteria}</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">{row.durable}</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">{row.framer}</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4 text-gray-900">{row.tenweb}</td>
                </tr>
              ))}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">5 Beginner Tips for Success</h2>

        {tips.map((tip, i) => (
          <div class="my-6 p-6 bg-white border-[3px] border-[#F5521A]/20">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-[#F5521A] text-white font-black flex items-center justify-center">
                {i + 1}
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg">{tip.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">{tip.content}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}

        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-6">Bottom Line for Beginners</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          <strong>Start with Durable AI.</strong> It's the easiest, fastest, most beginner-friendly option. Generate your site in 30 seconds, customize the text and images, launch.<br /><br />
          If you care about design and don't mind a slight learning curve, <strong>Framer AI</strong> creates better-looking sites.<br /><br />
          Only choose <strong>10Web AI</strong> if you specifically want WordPress. WordPress is powerful but adds complexity.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 mt-12 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-4">The Beginner Verdict</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6">
            Durable AI is the easiest choice for complete beginners. 30 seconds to a complete website, no tech skills required. Start with Durable, upgrade to Framer if you want more design control later.
          </p>
          <a href="/reviews/durable-ai" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#F5521A] text-white font-black border-[3px] hover:shadow-[0_6px_0_0_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] transition-all">
            Try Durable AI Free
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

</Layout>
